#atlantis 3 "111"

;*** forest (9,11) in Cehurst ***
; Turn 2 strategy: Study ILLU (PHEN prereq) at home. No gate-jump —
; GATE 1 is one-way, too risky. Scout Bosse and Nafirth with new units.
; Deploy tax garrison locally. Legatus moves to Bosse next turn.

unit 141
; Legatus (141) - Mage commander
; Study ILLU (only missing PHEN prereq). Halved rate: 15/30 days.
; Stay at (9,11) this turn, move to Bosse town (8,10) next turn.
CLAIM 1000
STUDY ILLU

; --- Form tax garrison: 5 centaurs, study COMB this turn, GUARD+TAX next ---
form 1
  NAME unit "Praesidium I"
  DESCRIBE unit "Tax garrison of the eternal legion"
  CLAIM 500
  BUY 5 CTAU
  BEHIND 0
  REVEAL NONE
  STUDY COMB
  turn
    @GUARD 1
    @TAX
  endturn
end

; --- Form scout: 1 centaur, move north to explore Nafirth ---
form 2
  NAME unit "Explorator I"
  DESCRIBE unit "Scout of the eternal legion"
  CLAIM 100
  BUY 1 CTAU
  BEHIND 1
  AVOID 1
  SPOILS NONE
  MOVE N
end

; --- Form scout: 1 centaur, move SW to explore southern Cehurst ---
form 3
  NAME unit "Explorator II"
  DESCRIBE unit "Scout of the eternal legion"
  CLAIM 100
  BUY 1 CTAU
  BEHIND 1
  AVOID 1
  SPOILS NONE
  MOVE SW
end

#end
